name: Vendugo car rental landing page
description:
Vendugo (Adventure do and go)

Is a website that provides services to prepare you to explore places and experiences that you have never done before

.

This is the result of my exploration to create a website that will primarily spread brand awareness. Its purpose is to clarify what the company does. In addition to the landing page, the website will need a contact page, product page and terms of service, The landing page should have a contact us section. There should be a call to action to get users to see the catalog they want in a monochromatic design, and want you to use the brand color, which is orange. Consider client preferences and values.
